      h2 ğŸ›ï¸ YOU ARE IN PRISON ğŸ›ï¸
      p The federal investigation into your megachurch empire has concluded, and you have been sentenced to prison for your crimes.

    template(v-if="!my.church.isFounded")
      p It's a shame that you never even got your Megachurch off the ground. The game is called #[strong Megachurch Tycoon] after all.
        span(v-if="!my.hasVan") And you didn't even get a van.
        span(v-else-if="my.chats.sterling.hasContacted") Maybe Sterling could have helped you out with that.
        span(v-else) You did manage to get a van, you should have held on just a little bit longer.

    p(v-if="!my.van") If you'd bought the van from Harold, you'd be able to preach in new places. And after a couple days of that, you'd probably have met somebody new.


    .game-over-stats
      table
        tbody
          tr
            td.label Total Days Survived:
            td.value {{my.daysPlayed}}
          tr(v-if="my.chats.sterling.hasContacted")
            td.label Sterling Status:
            td.value {{my.eternalLegacy.sterlingAlive ? 'alive' : 'dead'}}
          tr(v-if="my.eternalLegacy.isActive")
            td.label Final Mammon Score:
            td.value.huge {{addCommas(my.eternalLegacy.totalMammon)}}
          tr(v-if="my.totalMoneyEarned > 0")
            td.label Total Money Earned:
            td.value {{dollars(my.totalMoneyEarned)}}

    .purchased-items(v-if="my.eternalLegacy.purchasedItems.length > 0")
      h3 Your Legacy Items
      .items-list
        .mammon-items(v-if="purchasedMammonItems.length > 0")
          h4 ğŸ’° Mammon Collection
          ul
            li(v-for="item in purchasedMammonItems" :key="item.id") {{item.name}}
        
        .under-table-items(v-if="purchasedDarkDeeds.length > 0")
          h4 ğŸ”¥ Dark Deeds Arrangements
          ul
            li(v-for="item in purchasedDarkDeeds" :key="item.id") {{item.name}}

    .big-button-holder
      button.restart(@click="restartGame") Begin New Ministry